      • ITEM

        public ITEM(NCIntentSolver.Predicate pred,
            int min,
            int max)
        Creates new item with given parameters.
        Parameters:
        pred - Built-in token predicate: either one of the built-in logical combinators or RULE.
        min - Minimum (inclusive) number of times the token predicate pred should find a match in the user input for this item to match.
        max - Maximum (inclusive) number of times the token predicate pred should find a match in the user input for this item to match.
